    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This FD3S chassis exemplifies the pinnacle of 90s JDM engineering. Powered by the 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, this unit delivers linear power delivery across the rev range with a verified healthy compression profile. The front-midship engine placement ensures a perfect weight distribution, complemented by a factory-spec four-wheel double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential. Every component, from the intricate vacuum-controlled turbo sequencing to the untouched OEM drivetrain, operates with mechanical precision. This is a collector-grade survivor, free of chassis fatigue or aftermarket interference, representing a rare opportunity for the discerning purist.",
