    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S54 platform, featuring its iconic 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox with short, tactile throws and a fresh clutch. Mechanically, this vehicle is impeccable: the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings\u2014a critical maintenance item\u2014have been replaced with uprated components. The variable M differential lock provides exceptional traction out of corners, complemented by a suspension setup that retains its factory-spec damping and bushing integrity. Finished in its original paint with zero orange peel or swirl marks, the chassis remains rigid and free of any structural fatigue. A pristine collector-grade machine for the enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection.",
